snippet.title: Quake - Rapture (Part 2 of 4)
snippet.description:
Part two of me conquering Rapture. New in this level is an actual fight with a Shambler, introduction of the Vore, a small fight with what I can only guess is a Hell Lord, and a fray with the Gaurdian of Fire.

Rapture is a Quake episode by Tronyn and [Kona], released in September 2001. If you like this episode, be sure to check out [Kona]'s site at ethereal-hell.telefragged.com and visit Tronyn's Bazaar at tronyn.planetquake.gamespy.com.

Self Commentary:
It may be a bug in the programming, but while trying to record these demos some of the gremlins are being randomly activated while I'm not even in the area. They are starting to catch me off gaurd and I've had my weapon snatched right out of my hands on multiple occassions. They're pretty quick to dodge, but I am still quicker.
